Paper: 150905109
Title: Time-independent Hamiltonian for any linear constant-coefficient  evolution equation
Authors: Carl M. Bender and Mariagiovanna Gianfreda and Nima Hassanpour and Hugh F. Jones
Abstract: It is shown how to construct a time-independent Hamiltonian having only one degree of freedom from which an arbitrary linear constant-coefficient evolution equation of any order can be derived.
